      "updated": 1781568150846,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Goal: tweak ONE recipe (container naming) and redeploy.\n\nSupported flow today:\n  1. Get the default pack (CLI / sample artifact).\n  2. Copy & rename it; substitute the one recipe.\n  3. Deregister the default pack.\n  4. Register the new custom pack & redeploy.\n\nConstraints:\n  • Only ONE recipe per type per environment.\n  • You can't override/merge onto the default in place.\n  • Editing the default directly is NOT the model —\n    copy → rename → register instead.\n\nAsk: make the default discoverable + editable\n(CLI outputs Bicep/YAML, not just JSON).",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 14,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Goal: tweak ONE recipe (container naming) and redeploy.\n\nSupported flow today:\n  1. Get the default pack (CLI / sample artifact).\n  2. Copy & rename it; substitute the one recipe.\n  3. Deregister the default pack.\n  4. Register the new custom pack & redeploy.\n\nConstraints:\n  • Only ONE recipe per type per environment.\n  • You can't override/merge onto the default in place.\n  • Editing the default directly is NOT the model —\n    copy → rename → register instead.\n\nAsk: make the default discoverable + editable\n(CLI outputs Bicep/YAML, not just JSON).",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "aO",
      "autoResize": true
    },
